&quot;;\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">Repairing the artwork. If the damage is something the artist is able to repair, then the artist could offer this option to you. We will arrange the return of the artwork to the artist courtesy of Art<\\/span><span lang=\\\"EN-US\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">wex<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">, and will be able to repair it, and once you have confirmed you are happy with the repair, the artist will then reship the artwork to you.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 54.75pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 18.6pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">\\u00b7<span style=\\\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">A replacement. For certain artworks, such as prints, the artist may be able to offer you a replacement. We would proceed with a return as normal, but instead of refunding you, the artist would send you a replacement. The artist may also wish to offer you a commissioned piece in lieu of the damaged artwork if it\'s beyond repair.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 18pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18.6pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">It is important to note that these options are not mandatory, and if the artist is unable to offer any of the above, then you will be able to return the damaged artwork and receive a refund.<\\/span><\\/p><h1 style=\\\"margin: 0cm 22.5pt 6pt 0cm; font-size: 24pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 22.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-weight: normal;\\\">Delivery Exceptions<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/h1><p style=\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 18pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18.6pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">There may be occasions when your order is not delivered which could be for a number of reasons. When there are delivery exceptions, these will generally be visible on the&nbsp;tracking.&nbsp;<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><h4 style=\\\"margin: 6.75pt 0cm 7.8pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\">Order held at post office or couriers hub&nbsp;<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 18pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18.6pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">If an order is being held at your local post office or at the couriers hub, you will need to contact the courier or your local postal service in order to rearrange delivery, or to arrange a collection.&nbsp;<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><h4 style=\\\"margin: 6.75pt 0cm 7.8pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\">Order held at customs<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 18pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18.6pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">If an order is being held at customs, it could either be held pending charges, or, further information may be needed from the sender or the receiver in order for this to be cleared. In cases like these, we would encourage you to contact the courier directly regarding this. If you are in doubt about what they require, then you may wish to contact the artist and ask them to reach out to their courier to clarify.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 18pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18.6pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">As Art<\\/span><span lang=\\\"EN-US\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">wex<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\"> is neither the sender, nor the receiver, the couriers will not provide us any information relating to shipments so while we are happy to assist where possible, and provide any information you may need, we are unable to contact the courier ourselves.&nbsp;<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><h4 style=\\\"margin: 6.75pt 0cm 7.8pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\">Order returned to sender<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/h4><p style=\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 18pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18.6pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">If an order is being returned to the artist, they will need to ascertain why this is happening. Some of the reasons an order may be returned back to the artist are as follows:<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 54.75pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 18.6pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">\\u00b7<span style=\\\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">The courier tried to deliver but nobody was in to accept the parcel (they will usually have a maximum number of times they will attempt delivery before returning to sender).<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 54.75pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 18.6pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">\\u00b7<span style=\\\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">The shipping documentation was incomplete, and the courier hasn\\u2019t received the information they need in time.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 54.75pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 18.6pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">\\u00b7<span style=\\\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">There was an error with&nbsp;the shipping address.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 54.75pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 18.6pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">\\u00b7<span style=\\\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">There were&nbsp;pending import charges&nbsp;which weren\\u2019t paid in time, or the receiver refused delivery of the parcel due to not wanting to pay the import charges.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 18pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18.6pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">If an order is being returned to the artist, they will likely contact you to find out if you wish for this to be reshipped, or if you wish to receive a refund. If you notice that the tracking for your order says it has been returned to sender, and the artist has not contacted you, please contact our Support and Operations Team on customers@art<\\/span><span lang=\\\"EN-US\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">wex<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">.com.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 18pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18.6pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">In cases where the reason for the return is due to an issue such as&nbsp;the incorrect delivery address being given at checkout, or pending import charges not being paid on time, if you still wish to receive the artwork, then the cost of reshipping would fall to you. We would send you a PayPal invoice for additional shipping charges.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 18pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18.6pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">In cases where the reason for return is due to the shipping documentation being incomplete, or an error with the address made by the artist at the time of shipping, then the artist is likely to cover the new shipping charge should you still wish to receive the artwork.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 18pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18.6pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">If you wish to receive a refund for the returned order instead of having it reshipped, then please let the artist know, or contact Art<\\/span><span lang=\\\"EN-US\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">wex<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\"> directly and we will be able to process this.&nbsp;<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 18pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18.6pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">It is important to note that there may also be occasions where the tracking advises that your order has been delivered, but you haven\\u2019t received it. For further information on what to do if this is the case, please have a look here:&nbsp;I haven\'t received my order, but the tracking shows it\'s been delivered - what should I do?<\\/span><\\/p><h1 style=\\\"margin: 0cm 22.5pt 6pt 0cm; font-size: 24pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 22.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-weight: normal;\\\">I haven\'t received my order, but the tracking shows it\'s been delivered - what should I do?<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/h1><h3 style=\\\"margin: 6.75pt 0cm 7.8pt; break-after: avoid; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri Light&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 55, 99); line-height: 21pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\">How can I advise you that my order hasn\\u2019t arrived?<b><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/b><\\/span><\\/h3><p style=\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 18pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18.6pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">As you have access to the tracking details and the ETA (Estimated Time of Arrival) of your artwork through the order page, you are able to track your shipment with our integrated tracking system. Alternatively, you are able to use the tracking number provided by the artist on the nominated couriers website or&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.17track.net\\/en\\\" style=\\\"color: blue; text-decoration-line: underline;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: black;\\\">17TRACK<\\/span><\\/a>. We invite you to check the tracking information first and then notify the artist and our team of any delays which may have occurred in transit. Our team also monitors deliveries and therefore should an issue arise, we will reach out to you and the artist to offer assistance.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 18pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18.6pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">Alternatively, the artist may have shipped the order without tracking or did not provide a tracking number or courier. So in these cases, an automated delivery confirmation email will be sent to you three working days after the ETA provided on the order page. By clicking the link in the email, you will be able to advise our Support Team that your order has not yet been delivered. When we are notified that you marked your order as not delivered but the tracking shows successful delivery, we will be in touch to advise you further.&nbsp;<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 18pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18.6pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">As our artists are responsible for their shop\'s management and order fulfilment, we strongly recommend that you reach out to the artist via the messaging system to advise them of the non-delivery unless they have contacted you already.&nbsp;<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 18pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18.6pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(21, 33, 47);\\\">Once we are aware that your order has not been delivered, the order will be placed on hold for the duration of the investigation until we are able to confirm delivery.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><h3 style=\\\"margin: 6.75pt 0cm 7.8pt; break-after: avoid; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri Light&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 55, 99); line-height: 21pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\\\">What happens next?<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/h3><p style=\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 18pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18.6pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial;