\u043e\\u0440\\u0434\\u043e\\u043d\\u043e\\u043c.<\\/span><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p><p><span lang=\\\"UK\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;;\\\">\\u041c\\u0435\\u0448\\u043a\\u0430\\u0454 \\u0456 \\u043f\\u0440\\u0430\\u0446\\u044e\\u0454 \\u0445\\u0443\\u0434\\u043e\\u0436\\u043d\\u0438\\u0446\\u044f \\u0443 \\u043c\\u0456\\u0441\\u0442\\u0456 \\u041e\\u0434\\u0435\\u0441\\u0456.<\\/span><span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\\\"><\\/span><br><\\/p>\"}', NULL, 804, NULL, NULL, 'images/JptLTpRY7Pna97wjzSfidaycdd2FiB7BO4ubSCP0.png', 0, 0, 1, 9999, NULL, '2023-03-23 10:11:50', '2023-03-23 10:11:50');
INSERT INTO `shops` VALUES (17, NULL, '{\"en\":\"Natalia\",\"uk\":\"\\u041d\\u0430\\u0442\\u0430\\u043b\\u0456\\u044f\"}', '{\"en\":\"Konstanska\",\"uk\":\"\\u041a\\u043e\\u043d\\u0441\\u0442\\u0430\\u043d\\u0441\\u044c\\u043a\\u0430\"}', NULL, 'natalia', NULL, '{\"en\":\"<p>She was born in 1981 in Kyiv, in 1992 she moved to the city of Mariupol, to which she dedicated many of her works. Natalia Konstanska is an artist, works in the field of easel and monumental painting, decorative art, creates art objects. Creates paintings on canvas in the technique of oil, acrylic, often using potal. Conducts master classes with children. It draws inspiration from folk images, the beauty of nature, symbols and the history of ancient cultures. The creative path of the artist is aimed at the search for perfect performance, using new techniques, genres, directions. Her technically delicate works are filled with light, feelings, lyricism and frankness. Perfectly processes all the elements of the picture, trying to convey the smallest details of the plot. The paintings impress with their expressiveness, and sometimes with their mystery. He pays attention to the personalities of the heroes of his paintings, their own stories, and invests a deep philosophical meaning in his work. In 2015, she joined the organization \\\"League of Free Artists ARS ALTERA\\\" (Mariupol). In 2016, he became the leading artist of the \\\"Other Art\\\" project (Mariupol).<\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\">Cultural and artistic projects in which the artist took part with her works:<\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\">- Christmas exhibitions in the center of modern art and culture named after A. Kuindzhi, Mariupol (2017, 2019, 2020);<\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\">- the exhibition of modern art \\\"To the day of the city\\\" in the center of modern art and culture named after A. Kuindzhi, Mariupol (2018);<\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\">\\u2013 All-Ukrainian exhibition of women\'s portraits, Kyiv (2020);<\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\">\\u2013 exhibition \\\"EastFest\\\", Mariupol (2020);<\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\">\\u2013 \\\"POST MOST 2.0\\\" exhibition, Mariupol (2020);<\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\">\\u2013 exhibition \\\"Introversion\\\", Mariupol (2021);<\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\">\\u2013 \\\"POST MOST 3.0\\\" exhibition, Mariupol (2021);<\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\">\\u2013 the second all-Ukrainian triennial \\\"NY-ART\\\", Kremenchuk (2021);<\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\">\\u2013 a permanent exhibition of painting works by the League of Freelance Artists ARS ALTERA in the PortCity Shopping Center, Mariupol (2015-2022);<\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\">\\u2013 the exhibition \\\"Mariupol - an indomitable outpost of Ukraine\\\", Gdansk (2022);<\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\">- All-Ukrainian Patriotic Art Exhibition \\\"Unconquered Ukraine\\\", Kyiv (2022).<\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\">Unfortunately, most of the paintings were lost in the city of Mariupol during the hostilities.<\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\">Since the beginning of the war, the artist was in the city of Mariupol under constant fire, miraculously managed to evacuate. He continues to do his favorite business in the city of Kyiv, in order to continue to participate in art projects, preserve and develop the cultural heritage of Ukraine. It is creativity that helps to express lived experience and feelings.<\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height: 1;\\\">Currently, the artist lives and works in the city of Kyiv.<\\/p>\",\"uk\":\"<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 2;\\\"><span lang=\\\"UK\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 11pt;\\\">\\u041d\\u0430\\u0440\\u043e\\u0434\\u0438\\u043b\\u0430\\u0441\\u044f<\\/span><span lang=\\\"UK\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\\\"> <\\/span><span 